OL,3,CEnvironment Agency carrying out tests
OL,4,Cafter reports of black oil in River Wye
OL,6,FThe source of pollution in the River
OL,7,FWye is still not known, as Mark Gough
OL,8,Freports.
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency is testing the
OL,11,Fwater in the River Wye in Hereford
OL,12,Fafter reports of an oil spill on
OL,13,FSaturday afternoon.
OL,15,FAn oily substance could be seen on the
OL,16,Fsurface of the river over the weekend.
OL,18,FLocal angler, Phil Gammage first
OL,19,Fdiscovered the suspected spill.
