OL,3,CEnvironment Agency carrying out tests
OL,4,Cafter reports of black oil in River Wye
OL,6,FHe said: "I could smell it first, I
OL,7,Fcould smell a kerosene, oily smell and
OL,8,Fthen I saw a thick, black oil
OL,9,Fsubstance coming out of the culvert.
OL,11,F"It was jet black and it was filthy
OL,12,Fand smelly. It looked horrendous."
OL,14,FThe Environment agency has now put an
OL,15,Foil boom and absorbent pads at the
OL,16,Fsource of the pollution - a culvert at
OL,17,FRotherwas just outside Hereford.
