OL,3,CEnvironment Agency carrying out tests
OL,4,Cafter reports of black oil in River Wye
OL,6,FRobert Fox from the Old Harp Fishery
OL,7,Fnear Ross-on-Wye said he fears for the
OL,8,Fimpact of the suspected spill on
OL,9,Fwildlife.
OL,11,FHe added: "This is yet another threat,
OL,12,Fparticularly to water birds and to the
OL,13,Friver banks."
OL,15,FMike Mitchell, who teaches kayaking on
OL,16,Fthe river, said: "You could feel the
OL,17,Foil in the water, I tested a bit on my
OL,18,Flips and it burnt."
