OL,6,F"It feels really oily" - kayaking
OL,7,Fteacher tests the water in the River
OL,8,FWye
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency said: "The EA
OL,11,Fare continuing to investigate this
OL,12,Fincident and our staff have attended
OL,13,Fthe site three times over the holiday
OL,14,Fperiod."
OL,16,F"We are working closely with Welsh
OL,17,FWater, and have placed an oil boom and
OL,18,Fpads to contain and absorb the spill."
