OL,3,CEnvironment Agency carrying out tests
OL,4,Cafter reports of black oil in River Wye
OL,6,FAn investigation by ITV Central in May
OL,7,F2021 found some rivers in the Midlands
OL,8,Fwere carrying up to 50 times the safe
OL,9,Flevel of chemicals in the water.
OL,11,FIn September 2022, we revealed that in
OL,12,F2020 alone, 33 years worth of sewage
OL,13,Fwas dumped into the catchment area of
OL,14,Fthe River Wye, which runs through
OL,15,FHerefordshire.
